name: Têtes chercheuses 001
description: Têtes chercheuses by @nicobiev, is a serie of images taken at airshows, from which aircrafts have been removed.  What interests me here is the transformative power evoked by these aerial traces once planes are removed. They evoke a series of rockets equipped with homing heads, in search of a target of which we do not know the type and an action of which we do not know the nature. –Original image by Gian Marco Anzellotti under CC license Attribution 2.0 Generic (CC BY 2.0)
